# Super Dojo Project Structure

This is a React Native/Expo app with Convex backend for martial arts club management.

## Main Entry Points
- [App.tsx](mdc:App.tsx) - Root React Native component
- [index.ts](mdc:index.ts) - Metro bundler entry point

## Directory Structure

### Frontend (React Native/Expo)
- `src/screens/` - Main app screens (Home, Auth, Clubs, Events, etc.)
- `src/navigation/` - Navigation configuration with [AppNavigator.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/AppNavigator.tsx)
- `src/context/` - React contexts, including [AuthContext.tsx](mdc:src/context/AuthContext.tsx)
- `src/i18n/` - Internationalization with English and Finnish locales
- `src/test/` - Test utilities and setup

### Backend (Convex)
- `convex/` - Backend functions and database schema
- [convex/schema.ts](mdc:convex/schema.ts) - Database schema definitions
- [convex/auth.ts](mdc:convex/auth.ts) - Authentication functions
- [convex/clubs.ts](mdc:convex/clubs.ts) - Club management functions
- [convex/attendance.ts](mdc:convex/attendance.ts) - Attendance tracking
- [convex/clubFeed.ts](mdc:convex/clubFeed.ts) - Club feed and posts
- `convex/_generated/` - Auto-generated Convex types (regenerate with `npx convex dev`)

### Testing
- `e2e/` - End-to-end tests using Playwright
- `src/**/__tests__/` - Unit tests co-located with components

### Configuration
- [convex.json](mdc:convex.json) - Convex project configuration
- [app.json](mdc:app.json) - Expo app configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts

## Development Workflow
Refer to [DEVELOPMENT.md](mdc:DEVELOPMENT.md) for setup instructions. Key commands:
- `npm start` - Start Expo dev server
- `npx convex dev` - Start Convex backend
- `npm run seed` - Seed database with sample data
